👉 Attention All Job Seekers! This is for you.
 
 Thousands of job seekers in India are desperately searching for a new job but are unable to find one. 🔥
 
 Are you one of them?
 
 If yes, then listen carefully…
 
 Join me in my FREE upcoming Dream Job Webinar where I’ll share with you my top secrets regarding effective job search in the fast-changing hiring landscape.
 
 You’ll learn 3 things in this high-impact webinar that attendees are raving about:
 
 ✅ Why you’re not able to find a job right now. 
 ✅ How hiring takes place for top jobs.
 ✅ How to use a proven framework for successful job search in India.
 
 Click the ‘Sign Up’ button below and reserve your seat for this free webinar that may change your life forever.
 
 I’m Vikram Anand – a top career coach with over 31 years of experience in the Indian corporate sector at companies like Unilever, Johnson & Johnson, Nokia, and many others. 
 
 I’ve coached middle and senior level managers on job search strategies at elite institutions like the Indian School of Business in Hyderabad and Upgrad in Mumbai.
 
 My students have used the strategies from this webinar to get dream jobs at Amazon, KPMG, Deloitte, Goldman Sachs, Accenture, HP, L’Oreal and many other MNCs.
 
 Hurry and register now to attend the Dream Job Webinar at a date and time of your convenience.
 
 👉 Click ‘Sign Up’ now and reserve your seat.

Ghostwriting clients are EVERYWHERE.

Because anyone who wants to:

• Scale their knowledge…
• Attract new opportunities online…
• Sell more of their product or service…

Needs a ghostwriter.

Here are just a few examples of people who need to hire ghostwriters:

• CEOs
• Doctors
• Coaches
• Plumbers
• Musicians
• Nutritionists
• Yoga Instructors
• Green Energy scientists

In short, any business needs a ghostwriter to help communicate & scale their message and educate their customers.

So, that’s why I say ghostwriting clients are EVERYWHERE.

These people don’t have the time to write (or have the time to learn how to write) but they DO have knowledge they want to share and other people need. 

But the ghostwriter DOES have the time to write but doesn’t have the specific industry experience. 

It’s a perfect pairing.

In other words, there’s TONS of opportunity for ghostwriters out there right now.

And as the trend of people wanting to hear from individuals rather than companies accelerates, this opportunity to help people communicate and scale their message online is only going to grow.

So, it’s time to get started!
